title: Ten Must Have Essential Country Albums [-emidius-]
description:
The included are considered by many to be some of the top essential Country albums of all time. Regardless of any album rankings...these are truly MUST OWN albums for anyone interested in Country music. I hope you enjoy this collection and I will be releasing further collections in the near future.

01.Hank Williams 40 Greatest Hits released 1990



02.Marty Robbins Gunfighter Ballads and Trail Songs released in 1959



03.Ray Charles Modern Sounds in Country and Western Music released 1962



04.Patsy Cline 12 Greatest Hits released 1967



05.Johnny Cash Johnny Cash At Folsom Prison released 1968



06.The Nitty Gritty Dirt Band Will The Circle Be Unbroken released 1972



07.Leon Russell Retrospective 1970 - 1975



08.Gram Parsons Grievous Angel released 1974



09.Poet: A Tribute To Townes Van Zandt released 2001



10.The Secret Sisters The Secret Sisters released 2010
